s. <a title=\"BlogOhBlog\" href=\"http://www.blogohblog.com/\">BlogOhBlog</a></li><li><a title=\"ThemeJam\" href=\"http://themejam.com/\">ThemeJam</a> vs. <a title=\"Startbox\" href=\"http://wpstartbox.com/\">Startbox</a></li><li><a title=\"Organic Themes\" href=\"http://www.organicthemes.com/\">Organic Themes</a> vs. <a title=\"Storefront Themes\" href=\"http://storefrontthemes.com/\">Storefront Themes</a></li><li><a title=\"Theme Hybrid\" href=\"http://themehybrid.com/\">Theme Hybrid</a> vs. <a title=\"Xtreme Theme\" href=\"http://xtreme-theme.com/\">Xtreme Theme</a></li><li><a title=\"Pro Theme Design\" href=\"http://prothemedesign.com/\">Pro Theme Design</a> vs. <a title=\"Themes Kingdom\" href=\"http://www.themeskingdom.com/en/page/home/23\">Themes Kingdom</a></li><li><a title=\"Solostream\" href=\"http://www.solostream.com/\">Solostream</a> vs. <a title=\"ThemeShift\" href=\"http://themeshift.com/\">ThemeShift</a></li><li><a title=\"Crowd Favorite\" href=\"http://crowdfavorite.com/\">Crowd Favorite</a> vs. <a title=\"Working Wireframes\" href=\"http://workingwireframes.com/\">Working Wireframes</a></li></ul><p>All of the polls and instructions can be found just after the jump, so be sure to click through to have your voice heard. Voting will take place for the next 48 hours, and close at midnight on the 13th (Eastern Standard Time).</p><p>If you need a reminder, the rules can be found <a title=\"How to win your Theme Madness 2011 Trophy\" href=\"http://wpcandy.com/announces/theme-madness-2011-rules\">here</a>. Good luck to everyone playing!</p><p><span id=\"more-16870\"></span></p><h3>Graph Paper Press vs. Panda Themes</h3><p><a name=\"pd_a_4893015\"></a><div class=\"PDS_Poll\" id=\"PDI_container4893015\"></div><p><br /> <br /> <a href=\"http://polldaddy.com/poll/4893015/\">View This Poll</a><br /><br /><span><a href=\"http://polldaddy.com/features-surveys/\">online survey</a></span><br /> </p><p>Remember, along with this poll you can also vote two other ways: